des:
Now you can tell your devices how you would like them to behave. 

My Ivation products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off the device.

There’s no need to go to physically power on or off your device - just talk to Alexa on your Alexa enabled voice controlled devices. 

After connecting Alexa to your Ivation Smart products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "My Ivation" app in android or ios app store.
(2). Register one account in our "My Ivation" app;
(3). You need to have some My Ivation devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "My Ivation" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in “My Ivation" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app Store.
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "My Ivation" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "My Ivation", and you'll be navigated to My Ivation login page;
(9). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:

"Alexa, turn on the dehumidifier"
"Alexa, turn off the dehumidifier"

More skills and products are coming soon. 

Feel free to email us at info@myivation.com
